719848f-a.title: Manhattan: Fort Washington Aven - 187th Street (West)
719848f-a.text:
Fort Gashington Ave., north from, but not including West 187th Street.
On the left, appears Northern Ave., with the Hudson River in the background.
Plot shown includes the James Gordon Bennett Estate.
June 1919.
Cift of E. M. Jenks.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
